序输入。注2：source 字段为缓存 ID，同 source 字段的提交使用相同的缓存目录。注3：source 字段包含且仅包含一个字符 /，建议使用 domainId/pid。注4：测试数据的 etag 用来识别本地缓存的文件是否与云端一致，可使用 hash 或是修改时间的时间戳。"},"321":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge#测试数据下载","content":"若推送的评测任务中使用了的测试数据缺失，Judge 端会向 Web 请求缺失或是修改的文件。"},"322":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge#测试数据下载","content":"服务端返回如下："},"323":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/api/judge#评测结果上报","content":"除 key, domainId, rid 三个字段外，其他字段均为可选。关于 STATUS_CODE 含义请查看 hydro-dev/Hydro/packages/utils/lib/status 。当 key 为 end 时表示评测任务已经完成，结果确定，Web 端可进行 AC 数计量，登记成绩表等操作。"},"324":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"page","content":"权限节点","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV"},"325":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"Hydro 的权限使用位运算处理。例：若某用户具有 PRIV_EDIT_SYSTEM 与 PRIV_SET_PERM 权限，应设置为 (1<<0)|(1<<1) （即 3）"},"326":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"可以看 代码 中关于此部分的内容。"},"327":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/PERM_PRIV","content":"扩展阅读：权限结构"},"328":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"page","content":"数据库结构","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout"},"329":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#document","content":"document"},"330":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout#documentstatus","content":"document.status"},"331":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/dev/db-layout-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/dev