o/system/cdn","content":"如您希望改善 Hydro 的访问质量，在您的服务器带宽较小的情况下，您可以考虑使用内容分发网络，即 CDN ，通常情况下您仅需设置资源 CDN 即可大幅度改善访问质量，关于如何使用内容分发网络和使用中的任何问题请联系各大云厂商。"},"840":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"创建并配置好资源 CDN ，在控制面板中将 server.cdn 设置项修改为 CDN 域名。（如 https://cdn.hydro.ac/，以 / 结尾）。"},"841":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"如果您预算充足，可以使用全站 CDN。"},"842":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全站 CDN 配置较为繁琐，如您没有相关使用经验请仅建立并配置资源 CDN ，配置资源 CDN 在大部分情况下即可大幅度改善访问质量。\n因各服务商全站 CDN 配置方法不同，配置过程不同，需要配置的内容较多，以下仅为参考配置且配置补全，如果有任何问题建议先查阅云服务商文档及咨询云服务商工程师。"},"843":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存设置可以参考以下设置："},"844":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"类型"},"845":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"内容"},"846":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存行为"},"847":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全部文件"},"848":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全部文件"},"849":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"遵循源站"},"850":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"文件后缀"},"851":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/syste